extends layout

block content
  h1 Password Reset Request üîê
  
  p Hi #{firstName},
  
  p We received a request to reset the password for your RideFlex Pro account.
  
  p If you requested this password reset, click the button below to proceed:
  
  // üîß STYLED BUTTON INSTEAD OF PLAIN LINK
  div(style='text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;')
    a(
      href=url
      style=`
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.3);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      `
      onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#0056b3'; this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 6px 12px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.4)';"
      onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#007bff'; this.style.transform='translateY(0px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 8px rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.3)';"
    ) üîê Reset My Password
  
  // üîß ALTERNATIVE FALLBACK LINK
  div(style='text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; padding: 15px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #007bff;')
    p(style='margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d;') 
      | If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
    p(style='margin: 10px 0 0 0; word-break: break-all; font-family: monospace; font-size: 12px; background-color: #e9ecef; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px;')
      = url
  
  div(style='margin: 30px 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 8px;')
    p(style='margin: 0; color: #856404;')
      strong ‚è∞ Important: 
      | This link will expire in 
      strong 10 minutes
      |  for security reasons.
  
  div(style='margin: 20px 0; padding: 15px; background-color: #d1ecf1; border: 1px solid #bee5eb; border-radius: 8px;')
    p(style='margin: 0; color: #0c5460; font-size: 14px;')
      | üîí 
 
      strong Security Notice: 
      | If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged and your account stays secure.
  
  hr(style='margin: 30px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;')
  
  p Stay secure,
    br
    | 
    strong The RideFlex Pro Security Team
    br
    | 
    small(style='color: #6c757d;') This email was sent automatically. Please do not reply.
